  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_f9426414-c41b-4bd3-97e3-61cf7a270e90" class="text-block-content">
    <p>An ePortfolio marked as spam will display a warning message that it is only visible to admins and the author [1]. Authors cannot edit ePortfolios marked as spam.</p>
<p>To mark the ePortfolio as safe, click the <strong>Mark as Safe</strong> button [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view-safe-eportfolio" data-step-uuid="a25faf7a-6053-47f2-ac2b-d1514c35a891">
    <h2 id="view-safe-eportfolio" class="step-title screensteps-heading">View Safe ePortfolio</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/003/012/629/original/15062026-be4f-4af5-a62c-1cd986934f79.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
