  <div id="text-content_a1069a7d-8725-4521-8426-25bdd088dc1a" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Admins can mark any ePortfolio as spam, even if the ePortfolio is not listed on the ePortfolio Moderation page.</p>
<p>To mark an ePortfolio as spam, navigate to the ePortfolio and click the <strong>Mark as Spam</strong> button.</p>
  </div>
